title: German spiced stars
ingredients: ['50g unsalted butter', '300g caster sugar', '2 eggs', '1 egg yolk', '1 teaspoon lemon juice', '290g plain flour', '2 1/2 teaspoons baking powder', '1 1/4 teaspoons ground cinnamon', '1/4 teaspoon salt', '1/4 teaspoon ground nutmeg', '60g finely chopped walnuts']
